```
┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  🤖 Model Durumu                                               │
│                                                                │
│  ✅ Physics Model      (Ağırlık: 40%)                         │
│  ✅ LightGBM           (Ağırlık: 25%)                         │
│  ✅ XGBoost            (Ağırlık: 20%)                         │
│  ✅ Gradient Boosting  (Ağırlık: 10%)                         │
│  ✅ Random Forest      (Ağırlık: 5%)                          │
│                                                                │
│  [Modeli Eğit]                                                 │
└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

---

## API

```
POST /api/v1/predictions/predict
Body: { arac_id, sofor_id, mesafe_km, ton, ascent_m, descent_m }
→ { tahmini_tuketim, model_used }

GET /api/v1/predictions/time-series/forecast?arac_id=X
→ { forecast: [...], forecast_dates: [...], confidence_low, confidence_high, trend }

GET /api/v1/predictions/time-series/trend?arac_id=X&days=30
→ { trend, trend_tr, slope, current_avg, previous_avg }

GET /api/v1/predictions/ensemble/status
→ { models, weights, total_models }

POST /api/v1/predictions/train/{arac_id}?model_type=xgboost
POST /api/v1/predictions/time-series/train?arac_id=X&days=180&epochs=100
```
